title: AWS re:Invent 2025-Digital transformation excellence using agentic AI: From vision to victory-MAM204
title_cn: AWS re:Invent 2025-使用智能体AI实现数字化转型卓越：从愿景到胜利-MAM204
abstract: Discover how customers are leveraging AWS AI-driven solutions to accelerate their cloud transformation journey, moving beyond traditional migration and modernization to achieve digital transformation excellence. This session showcases real-world experiences where organizations have integrated AI-powered accelerators with AWS cloud services to achieve 3x faster migration timelines and drive unprecedented business value. Learn actionable strategies and see demonstrations of how a large transformation project can become a digital enterprise enabler for your organization,
abstract_cn: 了解客户如何利用AWS AI驱动的解决方案加速其云转型之旅，超越传统的迁移和现代化，实现卓越的数字化转型。本次会议展示了真实案例，组织如何将AI驱动的加速器与AWS云服务集成，实现3倍更快的迁移时间线并推动前所未有的业务价值。学习可操作的策略，并观看大型转型项目如何成为组织数字化企业推动者的演示。

presenter.name: Brad Sevenko
presenter.title: Head of Agentic AI Transformation, ES
